column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: MILKA CHOCOLATE TABLET MILK WITH HAZELNUTS AND TOFFEE, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622300280802
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sugar, palm oil, cocoa butter, HAZELNUTS, whey powder (from MILK), skimmed MILK powder, cocoa mass, glucose syrup, MILK fat, CREAM powder (1,5%), sweetened condensed skimmed MILK, HAZELNUT paste, humectant (glycerol), emulsifiers (SOYA lecithin, sunflower lecithin), invert sugar syrup, caramelized sugar syrup (0,4%), flavourings, salt. Milk chocolate contains: Cocoa solids 30% minimum. Milk solids 18% minimum. MAY CONTAIN WHEAT AND OTHER NUTS. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 07/26/2016
